==Bosnian==
===Etymology===
By combining [[crna#Bosnian|crni]] (''black'') and [[luk#Bosnian|luk]] (''onion'').  Literally:  ''black onion'', as opposed to ''white onion'' (''garlic'').
===Noun===
'''crni luk''' {{m}}
#[[onion]]
#(''literally'') [[black]] [[onion]]
[[Category:bs:Seasonings]]
[[Category:bs:Vegetables]]

